Name: Biometrics Reference Code
Description: Code referencing a patient's record in an external biometrics system

Name: NIF
Description: Numéro d'Identité Fiscale, The Haiti Tax Identification Number (NIF) is issued by the Direction Générale des Impôts (DGI) since 1987.  Any Haitian natural or legal person gets this 10-digit number.

Name: CIN
Description: Carte d'Identification Nationale, The Haiti national identification card is meant to replace the fiscal identity card.  Created 2005.

Name: ECID
Description: Code referencing a patient's record in the SEDISH Master Person Index (Enterprise Client ID)

Name: Ancien Numéro Dossier
Description: Used to register legacy dossier number
